  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Result 1: Increased food availability and income opportunity through fishing and agricultural activities for 1,000 HHs in Nyal and Katieth payams
1: Rapid assessment
2: Community mobilisation and selection of beneficiaries
3: Procurement of fishing nets for 500 HHs
4: Procurement of agricultural inputs (vegetable seeds and tools) for 500 HHs
5: Distribution of fishing nets and agricultural inputs
6: PDM and reporting
Result 2: &#x2022;Improved living conditions of 2,000 HHs through distribution of plastic sheeting for shelter, insecticide-treated mosquito nets and hygiene kits
1: Rapid assessment
2: Procurement of 2,000 plastics sheets and 2,000 mosquito nets for 2,000 HHs
3: Distribution of mosquito nets and plastics sheets
4: Distribution of hygiene kits
5: PDM and reporting
Result 3: &#x2022;2,000 HHs have improved access to safe drinking water and have a means to store water safely
1: Rapid assessment
2: Procurement of water purification tablets
3: Distribution of water purification tablets and sensitisation of the community on correct usage
4: Repair of 10 boreholes and provision of additional spare parts
5: Water management committee training
6: Hand pump mechanics training
7: PDM, reporting and evaluation</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To improve food security, living conditions and access to safe water
Result 1: Increased food availability and income opportunity through fishing and agricultural activities for 1,000 HHs in Nyal and Katieth payams
Result 2: Improved living conditions of 2,000 HHs through distribution of plastic sheeting for shelter, insecticide-treated mosquito nets and hygiene kits
Result 3: 2,000 HHs have improved access to safe drinking water and have a means to store water safely</narrative>
  </description>
